    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As you are getting attacked, you start to move with incredible speed, leaving afterimages with each step.</p><p>You give disadvantage to the triggering attack or first instance of an attack in case of multi attack jutsu or skills, if it is a saving throw type of attack you gain a bonus of +2 to your saving throw as long as it is a physical saving throw.</p><p>If the target misses thanks to this jutsu, you appear 5ft. behind your target and have advantage to the next claw attack.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> for each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, the chakra cost increases by 3, raise the amount of attack you give disadvantage to by 1. At A rank the bonus to saving throw becomes a +3</p>",
